<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Executive IT — Conformité DORA</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --navy: #0a192f;
      --gold: #c5a059;
      --slate: #64748b;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --dora-blue: #1e3a8a;
      --dora-purple: #581c87;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--navy); display: flex; }

    /* Sidebar Corporate */
    .sidebar { width: 280px; height: 100vh; background: var(--navy); color: white; position: sticky; top: 0; padding: 40px 0; }
    .logo { padding: 0 30px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .logo h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; display: block; }

    .nav-item { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; color: #cbd5e1; transition: 0.3s; border-left: 3px solid transparent; }
    .nav-item.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: white; border-left-color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

    /* Main */
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 60px; max-width: 1400px; }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy); padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; }

    /* DORA Pillars Grid */
    .panel { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .panel-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--dora-blue); padding-left: 15px; }

    .dora-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .dora-pillar { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
    .pillar-icon { font-size: 20px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .pillar-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.2; }
    .pillar-score { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; color: var(--navy); }

    /* Compliance Table */
    .table-dora { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .table-dora th { text-align: left; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--slate); padding: 12px; background: #f8fafc; }
    .table-dora td { padding: 14px 12px; font-size: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

    .cost-box { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 700; }
    .dev-note { font-style: italic; color: var(--slate); font-size: 11px; display: block; margin-top: 4px; }
    
    .status-pill { padding: 4px 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .status-conform { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .status-gap { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }

    /* Summary Footer */
    .dora-footer { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .summary-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--navy); }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>Executive IT</h1>
      <span>Architecture & Gouvernance</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-item">Vue Stratégique</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Portefeuille Apps</div>
    <div class="nav-item">TRM — Risques</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Finance IT</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Cyber : IAM & Accès</div>
    <div class="nav-item active">Conformité DORA</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Sourcing & Vendors</div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <header class="header">
      <h2>Conformité DORA</h2>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate);">RÉSILIENCE OPÉRATIONNELLE NUMÉRIQUE</div>
    </header>

    <div class="dora-grid">
      <div class="dora-pillar">
        <div class="pillar-label">Gestion des Risques TIC</div>
        <div class="pillar-score">82%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dora-pillar">
        <div class="pillar-label">Gestion des Incidents</div>
        <div class="pillar-score">95%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dora-pillar">
        <div class="pillar-label">Tests de Résilience</div>
        <div class="pillar-score">64%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dora-pillar">
        <div class="pillar-label">Risques Tiers (ICT)</div>
        <div class="pillar-score">71%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dora-pillar">
        <div class="pillar-label">Partage d'Information</div>
        <div class="pillar-score">40%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-title">Pilotage Budgétaire & Opérationnel par Pilier</div>
      <table class="table-dora">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Exigence DORA</th>
            <th>Criticité</th>
            <th>Coût Pilotage</th>
            <th>Informations Services Dev/Ops</th>
            <th>État de Conformité</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Tests TLPT</strong><br><small>Tests de pénétration avancés</small></td>
            <td style="color:var(--dora-purple); font-weight:700;">TRÈS HAUTE</td>
            <td class="cost-box">210k €</td>
            <td><span class="dev-note">"Nécessite des prestataires externes certifiés."</span></td>
            <td><span class="status-pill status-gap">Gap identifié</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Registre des Tiers</strong><br><small>Cartographie Cloud/SaaS</small></td>
            <td style="color:var(--navy); font-weight:700;">HAUTE</td>
            <td class="cost-box">145k €</td>
            <td><span class="dev-note">"Finalisation de l'inventaire des sous-traitants ICT."</span></td>
            <td><span class="status-pill status-conform">Conforme</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>BCP / DR Plan</strong><br><small>Continuité d'activité</small></td>
            <td style="color:var(--dora-purple); font-weight:700;">CRITIQUE</td>
            <td class="cost-box">380k €</td>
            <td><span class="dev-note">"Tests de bascule multi-région réussis."</span></td>
            <td><span class="status-pill status-conform">Conforme</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Reporting Incidents</strong><br><small>Standardisation de l'alerte</small></td>
            <td style="color:var(--navy); font-weight:700;">MOYENNE</td>
            <td class="cost-box">95k €</td>
            <td><span class="dev-note">"Automatisation des rapports vers les autorités."</span></td>
            <td><span class="status-pill status-conform">Conforme</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="dora-footer">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">Synthèse pour le Comité d'Audit</div>
        <div class="summary-text">
          L'enveloppe globale de mise en conformité DORA pour 2026 est estimée à <strong>830k €</strong>. 
          Le point d'attention majeur concerne les <strong>tests TLPT</strong> (Threat Led Penetration Testing) dont la mise en œuvre nécessite une expertise externe non budgétisée initialement. 
          La résilience sur les tiers (Cloud) est sous contrôle grâce au renforcement des clauses contractuelles.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel" style="background: var(--navy); color: white;">
        <div class="panel-title" style="color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold);">Action Prioritaire</div>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;">Lancement de l'appel d'offres pour les tests de résilience avancés (TLPT) avant la fin du Q2.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 10px;">
          Impact Réglementaire : Élevé <br>
          Échéance : 17 Janvier 2025 (Application DORA)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
